			<p><img src="images\TriangleChoke.jpg" alt="TriangleChoke" style="float:left"><h1>Triangle Choke</h1>
			Head and arm choke using legs, Setup from armbar position with op gable gripping arms together.</br>
			If we are tyring to armbar ops right arm, your right arm goes through linked arms to elbow and grab the inside of your left knee,</br>
			Lean to the left and create an opening in ops arms so your right foot can go through, foot to floor next to ops left ear,</br>
			Move your left leg away from ops face to next to top of ops head, they should sit up a bit, help them, then side left leg under and lock the triangle</br>
